  "title": "YAPPERS WANTED",
  "description": "<p>🔥 <strong>No Experience Needed! Build a Career You’re Excited About</strong> 🔥</p><p><strong>About Us:</strong><br />We work closely with established and well-known brands, supporting their growth through creative and strategic face-to-face marketing initiatives. As part of a dynamic and fast-growing organisation, we provide real-world exposure, strong mentorship, and opportunities to grow from the ground up.</p><p><strong>Your Role:</strong><br />🎉 <strong>Events & Campaigns</strong> – Be involved in marketing campaigns, brand activations, and on-ground projects.<br />🤝 <strong>Customer Engagement</strong> – Create positive brand experiences and build strong connections through face-to-face interactions.<br />🕴️ <strong>Professional Development</strong> – Develop confidence, communication, and leadership skills while representing brands with professionalism.</p><p><strong>What You’ll Gain:</strong><br />💎 <strong>Career Progression</strong> – Clear development pathways with opportunities to step into leadership roles.<br />📈 <strong>Mentorship & Growth</strong> – One-to-one coaching, guidance, and hands-on learning from day one.<br />🌏 <strong>Travel Exposure</strong> – Regional and international opportunities as you grow with the team.<br />🌟 <strong>Supportive Culture</strong> – A positive, collaborative, and high-energy environment that pushes you to be your best.<br />💰 <strong>Performance-Based Rewards</strong> – Recognition and incentives aligned with your growth and performance.</p><p><strong>Additional Details:</strong><br />📍 Location: Hybrid (Based in Singapore)<br />🗓 Schedule: Monday to Friday<br />🚀 Start Date: Immediate / Short Notice Available</p><p>🌱 <strong>No prior experience required.</strong> We value attitude, drive, and a willingness to learn. Training and support will be provided from day one.</p><p><strong>Ready to step out of routine and into growth?</strong><br />Join us and see how far your potential can take you!</p>",
